Before attending the workshop, please have the following ready.

1. Bring a laptop for the hands-on analyses.

2. Install required R packages in advance.
  2-1. for the Session 2
       if (!requireNamespace("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE)){install.packages("BiocManager")}
       BiocManager::install("microbiome")

       if (!requireNamespace("devtools", quietly = TRUE)){install.packages("devtools")}
       devtools::install_github("jbisanz/qiime2R")

       install.packages(c("phyloseq","ggplot2","vegan"))

  2-2. for the Session 3
       install.packages(c("iCAMP","reshape2","dplyr","ape"))

